name: BABY HIPPO
description: Introducing Baby Hippo BabyHippo is a Meme project supported and loved by the community. Baby Hippo has arrived to represent the hippopotamus in the memecoin movement on BSC. No Cats, No Dogs, Only Baby Hippo! The market is saturated with Cats and Dogs; it's time for Hippo to take the stage. Baby Hippo is poised to lead a powerful wave on the Binance Smart Chain. Baby Hippo's Journey on Binance Smart Chain.
